y to provide access screening and denied the messages were obscene. <PERSON> Intercambio </PERSON> also argued that it had not violated the regulation because it never intended to transmit interstate or to minors. The commission staff is investigating complaints about two other dial-a-porn companies, <ORGANIZATION> Ramrod </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Enterprises </ORGANIZATION><ORGANIZATION> , </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Inc. </ORGANIZATION> and 2001 Enterprises.
