ION>, one of the 40,000 spectators at the stadium. `` I do n't believe in nostalgia,'' she said. `` People have to go forward.'' The military show, one of the most elaborate in <LOCATION> Israel </LOCATION>'s history, was broadcast live <PERSON> Herzog </PERSON> held a reception for veterans of the Indpendence war. <LOCATION> Israel </LOCATION> became independent on May 14, 1948, which corresponds with April 21 on this year's Jewish calendar, and the armies of <LOCATION> Egypt </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Iraq </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Lebanon </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Syria </LOCATION> and <LOCATION> Jordan </LOCATION> invaded on the same day.
